us-power-budget-phones-camera-battery-life-upgrades|title=The Moto G Stylus and G Power make Motorola\u2019s best budget phones even better|work=[[The Verge]]|last=Gartenberg|first=Chaim|date=7 February 2020|accessdate=8 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Release ==\nThe G8 Plus and Play were announced in October 2019 and released in October and November 2019 in Europe and Latin America; an international version was also released. Both devices are not available in the United States, however the G8 Power and G Stylus will be.\n\n== Specifications ==\nSome specifications such as wireless technologies and storage will differ between regions.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\nComparison of specifications between the models\n!\n!G8 Play<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.motorola.com.br/smartphone-moto-g8-play/p|title=Novo Moto G8 Play com c\u00e2mera tripla {{!}} Smartphones Motorola - Motorola|website=www.motorola.com.br|access-date=2019-11-23|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/motorola_moto_g8_play-9918.php|title=Motorola Moto G8 Play - Full phone specifications|website=www.gsmarena.com|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n!G8<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.motorola.com.br/smartphone-moto-g8/p|title=Novo motorola moto g8: sistema multic\u00e2meras {{!}} Loja Motorola Oficial|website=www.motorola.com.br|access-date=2020-03-05|language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/motorola_moto_g8-10051.php|title=Motorola Moto G8 - Full phone specifications|website=www.gsmarena.com|access-date=2020-03-05}}</ref>\n!G8 Plus<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.motorola.co.uk/smartphones-moto-g-plus-gen-8/p?skuId=153|title=moto g8 plus - Motorola UK|website=www.motorola.co.uk|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gsmarena.com/motorola_moto_g8_plus-9916.php|title=Motorola Moto G8 Plus - Full phone specifications|website=www.gsmarena.com|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n!G Power<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.motorola.com/us/products